Relation between Homeless and Unemployment

Focus: Is there a relationship between homelessness and unemployment rate?

This repository contains all the R files that were produced to clean up mutiple csv files and a master csv file for visualization purpose; including identify the relationship using visualization technique.

The Result of Each File will Produce
  1. Homeless_work file
  2. Unemployment_work file
  3. Homeless_unemploy_clean file
  4. Pop-work file
  5. Avg-work file
  6. Joint_data_work file
  7. Final Result of the Table
